caption: Burgundy is the color to invest in for the season ahead. Effortlessly straddling the line between a pop and a neutral, it’s a versatile color that transitions effortlessly from runway to real life—softer and easier to wear than a bright red, yet more impactful than your classic black or brown.  Discover seven chic ways to wear it this winter, from cozy knits to statement coats, at the link in bio.
